For your Emmy consideration for best directing in a comedy series. @netflix MO episode 7 -  Testimony. I chose this episode out of the whole season because I felt it was a true authentic view into the flaws of immigration court and how frustrating it can be for immigrants who’ve waiting years to get there. It’s something I’ve never seen on TV and to be able to tell this story with some levity and duality of tones made it feel like the best choice. Thanks for the support! 

#gettingtothedirecting #emmys #monetflix #director #filmmaker #comedy #drama
